{"tid":1522780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【《環時》假新聞】獨家報道「黃之鋒」被捕 眾志副主席：唔係佢嚟","createTime":"2019-08-31T14:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T01:09:53.000Z","uid":68738,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8c3daea5f2959c758afc3d5e5ebcb7608c446e","tid":1522780,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進近日親自「出征」香港，到反送中示威前線採訪，卻老貓燒鬚！《環球時報》今晚9時48分「搶先」在一眾香港媒體報道前，以快訊方式指，昨日才被港警拘捕的香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，今晚9時30分在銅鑼灣又被香港警方「抓獲」。報道還附上一段短片，片中有一名貌似黃之鋒的男子被警方帶走。不過，香港眾志副主席鄭家朗接受《蘋果》記者訪問時表示，該名被捕男子並非黃之鋒，而黃之鋒已被保釋外出，目前未有資料證實他有否到過銅鑼灣。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》今晚在官微發佈這則新聞時，特別以標誌是「獨家」新聞，並指據《環球時報》記者了解，警方逮捕黃之鋒的理由是「參加未經批准的集會」。報道最後還加了一句「抓了放，放了再抓」。怎料原來是擺烏龍，短片中的男子雖貌似黃之鋒，身形卻明顯比他壯健。但也不排除《環球時報》故意張冠李戴，製造假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者／新浪微博<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190831/large/1567260630_6669.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190831%2Flarge%2F1567260630_6669.jpg&h=37749925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（右圖）黃之鋒被《文匯報》拍到在銅鑼灣現身，但環球網晚上報道黃之鋒被捕，其衣着並不相符。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190831/59996118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190831%2F59996118&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=bdf6ecdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190831%2F59996118&h=acaf84bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190831/59996118</a>"},{"pid":"85ac2ec0d90db04f356341dce3a526aa38edd7ef","tid":1522780,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bb4f4f283dc742abf0253a189c5a6cca0347b9","tid":1522780,"uid":78947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"又真係幾似"},{"pid":"9cefdb040d1b93d19c1091fb7c3417a25998ff26","tid":1522780,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:32:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"50ff020679c2b51b612fbecd00d4e412c77c64d6","tid":1522780,"uid":187861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdf806399277f49bd158c7f8a3f0e475006d502","tid":1522780,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"又真係有少少似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前線嘅手足唔好再等後面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1522683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1522683</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ce4f03a5fd4df3c0224bdab44f4c3383e7f04e3","tid":1522780,"uid":304306,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪得我一個<br />\n我覺得似劉馬車多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8ee2c767e1eb2937ecb1eb70abcf44c0b98d13","tid":1522780,"uid":212897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif